1
00:01:24,839 --> 00:01:25,319
President Gu

2
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,559
Why are you here?

3
00:01:29,080 --> 00:01:29,839
Why are you back so late?

4
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,080
Is something wrong?

5
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:36,120
I...

6
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,959
I have a question for you.

7
00:01:41,279 --> 00:01:42,120
And this question...

8
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:45,080
Is a very serious and earnest one.

9
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:47,239
Let's talk upstairs.

10
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,360
It's not raining anymore, why the umbrella?

11
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,040
I think you're really out of your mind.

12
00:02:01,839 --> 00:02:02,440
Tell me.

13
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,000
What is it exactly?

14
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,320
You and Du Zheng,

15
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,320
and Feng Ziang,

16
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,320
have known each other for over 20 years?

17
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,119
Yeah.

18
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:15,919
We've known each other for 24 years.

19
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:18,080
Because our fathers knew each other.

20
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,520
Then Director Feng has been...

21
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,639
pursuing you lately.

22
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,679
Any thoughts on that?

23
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:26,960
To me,

24
00:02:30,119 --> 00:02:31,839
Du Zheng will be in my heart forever.

25
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,160
No one can ever replace him.

26
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,199
Let me ask... ask one more question.

27
00:02:38,119 --> 00:02:39,199
You must answer it carefully.

28
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:42,759
Back when I had my heart surgery,

29
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:44,279
right after I was discharged,

30
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,839
the first time you saw me,

31
00:02:46,839 --> 00:02:48,240
did you have any special thoughts?

32
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:50,399
What special thoughts?

33
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,160
I mean, when you saw me,

34
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:54,839
did you feel I looked a lot like...

35
00:02:56,199 --> 00:02:57,039
someone?

36
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:59,240
Like someone?

37
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,880
Did you feel I looked a lot like...

38
00:03:03,199 --> 00:03:04,119
someone you know?

39
00:03:08,839 --> 00:03:09,360
No.

40
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:10,720
Wait.

41
00:03:11,559 --> 00:03:13,320
Isn't it a good thing she didn't think of anyone else?

42
00:03:14,399 --> 00:03:15,639
It means in her heart,

43
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,919
I'm not a replacement for Du Zheng.

44
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,720
Besides,

45
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:22,919
there are very few people with a personality like yours.

46
00:03:23,559 --> 00:03:24,600
You're so handsome,

47
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,759
and so refined.

48
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,399
The refined type

49
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,839
is very popular right now.

50
00:03:29,119 --> 00:03:29,559
Right.

51
00:03:31,559 --> 00:03:32,479
I think,

52
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,679
compared to looks,

53
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,039
what's inside is more important.

54
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:41,600
So you're saying,

55
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:43,119
the police didn't find any blood

56
00:03:43,119 --> 00:03:43,720
in Tan Feng's car?

57
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,199
Right.

58
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,080
That's what my source said too.

59
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:47,720
This Tan Feng,

60
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,639
has been cleared of suspicion for a long time.

61
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,839
He might be an accomplice,

62
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,839
but he can't be the real killer.

63
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,279
How did it end up like this?

64
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,440
All the suspects

65
00:03:58,679 --> 00:03:59,800
have been cleared of suspicion.

66
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,440
I wonder what the police

67
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:04,720
will do next.

68
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,199
Is this Lin Yaoyao

69
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,679
actually doing her job properly?

70
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,279
The first time I saw that woman,

71
00:04:13,399 --> 00:04:14,600
I thought she was unreliable.

72
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:15,399
Makes sense.

73
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:15,960
Useless.

74
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,679
Makes sense.

75
00:04:16,679 --> 00:04:17,440
Stupid.

76
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:18,239
Makes sense.

77
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:19,600
Let's drive.

78
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,359
Because he's a murder suspect now,

79
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,440
the police will be watching him closely.

80
00:04:30,399 --> 00:04:31,320
So you must be careful.

81
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,799
Also, help me check

82
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:36,000
when the police surveillance will be looser.

83
00:04:36,359 --> 00:04:37,679
I don't care what method you use,

84
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:39,519
you must complete this mission.

85
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,399
Okay.

86
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,200
Got it.

87
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:49,760
Hello, Dad.

88
00:04:49,959 --> 00:04:50,760
Ziang.

89
00:04:51,799 --> 00:04:53,040
When are you coming back?

90
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,640
I'm out discussing business.

91
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,799
It might take about two hours.

92
00:04:58,679 --> 00:04:59,359
Well...

93
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:01,239
I want to go back for a bit.

94
00:05:02,359 --> 00:05:03,799
Before I return to Tongzhou,

95
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,440
I have some things

96
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,679
I want to talk to you about.

97
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:08,279
If you're not in a hurry,

98
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,720
how about waiting for me at home?

99
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,119
We can talk when I get back.

100
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,079
Ziang,

101
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:15,440
I'm quite bored alone at home.

102
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,720
I was just thinking

103
00:05:18,559 --> 00:05:20,000
you could keep me company and chat.

104
00:05:21,799 --> 00:05:22,679
Then I'll head back now.

105
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:27,320
The unqualified raw materials incident...

106
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,000
Don't you want to explain it to me?

107
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,720
As the son of a factory guard,

108
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:35,279
if I want to fight the chairman,

109
00:05:36,119 --> 00:05:37,079
I must find a

110
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:37,959
more powerful backer.

111
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:40,040
Are you out of your mind?

112
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,160
You weren't like this before.

113
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:44,040
How did you become like this?

114
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,839
People change.

115
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,359
I did it.

116
00:05:48,799 --> 00:05:50,359
Because you're my brother since childhood,

117
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:52,480
I'm admitting it to you.

118
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:55,040
Now you only have two choices.

119
00:05:55,679 --> 00:05:57,279
Either turn yourself in for leniency,

120
00:05:57,679 --> 00:05:58,239
or

121
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,679
wait for me to report you.

122
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:24,640
Gaoming,

123
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,600
you said Du Zheng's phone

124
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,480
suddenly has a signal?

125
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,040
What's going on?

126
00:06:27,359 --> 00:06:28,279
The telecom company sent a message.

127
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,119
They said Du Zheng's phone was turned on at night.

128
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,200
And the base station that received the signal

129
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,119
is a new one.

130
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:34,239
Yuhe District, Tongzhou City.

131
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:34,839
Yes.

132
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:36,559
We also found an important piece of information.

133
00:06:36,799 --> 00:06:38,600
Within a one-kilometer radius of this base station,

134
00:06:38,799 --> 00:06:40,000
is someone's hometown.

135
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:41,799
Guess who?

136
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,000
Who?

137
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,320
Feng Ziang.

138
00:06:52,359 --> 00:06:52,959
Dad,

139
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,720
I'm back.

140
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,359
Ziang,

141
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,839
those things you did,

142
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,480
I know all about them.

143
00:07:15,839 --> 00:07:17,399
Tomorrow I'll go find Yaoyao

144
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:18,600
and tell her about this.

145
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,359
Even if you cut ties with me.

146
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:27,839
Wake up!

147
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:28,720
Wake up!

148
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,359
Save him quickly!

149
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,320
He'll die if we don't save him!

150
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,760
Call 120!

151
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,119
You can't call!

152
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,679
He'll die right away without rescue!

153
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,520
Only one can live between Du Zheng and us.

154
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:41,760
Choose for yourself.

155
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,159
What are you thinking?

156
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:44,400
Have you forgotten?

157
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:46,159
I paid off hundreds of thousands in gambling debts for you.

158
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:48,039
Your wife's living and medical expenses...

159
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,239
We need to calculate it all.

160
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:52,000
Du Zheng already knows everything.

161
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,760
We caused the unqualified raw materials incident.

162
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,960
He knows it all.

163
00:08:55,239 --> 00:08:56,280
If you revive him,

164
00:08:56,599 --> 00:08:57,960
we'll have to go to jail.

165
00:08:59,159 --> 00:08:59,799
Go to jail?

166
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,080
I won't go to jail!

167
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,039
I won't go to jail!

168
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,280
I won't go to jail!

169
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,119
Then listen to me now.

170
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:06,320
Listen to me.

171
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:07,960
Just pretend nothing happened.

172
00:09:08,119 --> 00:09:09,200
Don't tell anyone anything.

173
00:09:09,599 --> 00:09:10,280
I promise you,

174
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:11,559
after this is over,

175
00:09:12,159 --> 00:09:13,559
I'll take your wife abroad for treatment.

176
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:14,880
And your child,

177
00:09:15,119 --> 00:09:16,799
I guarantee they'll be well-fed and clothed for life.

178
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:18,200
Do you understand?

179
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:19,760
Do you understand?

180
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,679
Do you understand?

181
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,799
I understand.

182
00:09:28,719 --> 00:09:29,479
Understood.

183
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:31,840
Let's go!

184
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:33,119
Let's go!

185
00:09:45,239 --> 00:09:46,039
An untaught son

186
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:47,679
is the father's fault.

187
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:50,520
I feel ashamed of you,

188
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,080
and sad for myself.

189
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:56,080
If you still have a little conscience left,

190
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:57,320
spend the rest of your life

191
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,919
paying for your blood debt.

192
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,760
Treat Jiaqi and old Du

193
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,479
a little better.

194
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:11,840
Feng Wei!

195
00:10:12,239 --> 00:10:12,880
Feng Wei!

196
00:10:15,719 --> 00:10:16,200
Feng Wei!

197
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:16,679
Keep up.

198
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:20,159
Go check inside.

199
00:10:22,119 --> 00:10:22,599
Feng Wei!

200
00:10:23,479 --> 00:10:24,039
Is anyone there?

201
00:10:25,919 --> 00:10:26,520
Senior!

202
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:36,799
Hurry!

203
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:37,760
Call an ambulance!

204
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:38,440
Hurry up!

205
00:10:39,119 --> 00:10:39,960
Hello, is this the hospital?

206
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,760
This is Yuhe District, Tongzhou City.

207
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,159
We have someone who needs emergency care.

208
00:11:04,679 --> 00:11:05,200
Secretary Peng.

209
00:11:05,479 --> 00:11:06,039
I'm here.

210
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:07,479
Is your last name Peng?

211
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:08,840
Help me send the data over.

212
00:11:09,599 --> 00:11:09,960
Okay.

213
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:10,760
Secretary Lin.

214
00:11:11,159 --> 00:11:11,679
It's time.

215
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,640
Let's go to the Tongzhou factory.

216
00:11:13,119 --> 00:11:13,520
Okay.

217
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:15,880
What about me?

218
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:16,760
You...

219
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,039
change the flowers in this vase.

220
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,799
Such a difficult job.

221
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,280
Excuse me.

222
00:11:27,039 --> 00:11:27,840
Hello, Yaoyao.

223
00:11:28,119 --> 00:11:29,080
I'm at work right now.

224
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:30,080
Let's talk later.

225
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:33,280
What did you say?

226
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:40,320
Yaoyao!

227
00:11:40,479 --> 00:11:41,239
How is it?

228
00:11:44,119 --> 00:11:44,599
Mr. Du,

229
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,320
the phone has been recovered.

230
00:11:50,919 --> 00:11:52,359
The truck involved in the accident is scrapped.

231
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,599
This is the only evidence we have right now.

232
00:11:55,559 --> 00:11:57,039
And we've done a blood test.

233
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,440
It proves it's Du Zheng's phone.

234
00:12:02,239 --> 00:12:02,840
But...

235
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,960
how did he hit my Du Zheng?

236
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,559
I saw in the confession letter that

237
00:12:13,719 --> 00:12:15,719
he was on his way to deliver a wallet to Feng Ziang

238
00:12:16,599 --> 00:12:17,640
when he hit Du Zheng.

239
00:12:19,719 --> 00:12:21,119
The phone kept ringing at the time.

240
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:23,000
He was afraid someone would see it,

241
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:23,919
so he took it away.

242
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:30,400
Mr. Du,

243
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:33,359
right now,

244
00:12:34,799 --> 00:12:35,760
all the evidence

245
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:36,799
points entirely to

246
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:37,479
Feng Wei.

247
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,080
I'm afraid the case will be closed.

248
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:41,919
I'm sorry.

249
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:56,320
Could he really be the killer?

250
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,960
Did he just have a driving accident,

251
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:04,479
or did he intentionally use the car to kill?

252
00:13:06,599 --> 00:13:07,400
Who are you?

253
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:08,760
Who are you?

254
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:10,080
Who are you?

255
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:14,559
No.

256
00:13:16,599 --> 00:13:17,520
I feel like it shouldn't be him.

257
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:21,599
Something must have gone wrong here.

258
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:29,280
Hello?

259
00:13:29,559 --> 00:13:29,960
Who is it?

260
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,119
Officer Lin,

261
00:13:31,719 --> 00:13:33,599
this is Gu Tiancheng.

262
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:35,719
I'm at the police station right now,

263
00:13:35,719 --> 00:13:36,679
waiting for you in the garden next door.

264
00:13:37,239 --> 00:13:37,840
Come see me immediately.

265
00:13:38,719 --> 00:13:39,400
Right now, immediately.

266
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:44,960
What is this guy doing?

267
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,440
Being so mysterious late at night.

268
00:14:02,039 --> 00:14:03,400
What do you want from me, kid?

269
00:14:05,559 --> 00:14:06,239
I asked you here

270
00:14:06,559 --> 00:14:07,359
to tell you

271
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,640
that the hit-and-run,

272
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,880
the case of Du Zheng's murder,

273
00:14:12,119 --> 00:14:13,280
wasn't done by Feng Wei.

274
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,000
What are you talking about?

275
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,239
At the time, I felt

276
00:14:19,359 --> 00:14:20,520
there was something wrong with that truck.

277
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:22,679
The vehicle probably wasn't a truck.

278
00:14:26,119 --> 00:14:26,919
Your police department

279
00:14:26,919 --> 00:14:28,000
wouldn't close the case so hastily, right?

280
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,960
You'll reopen the investigation, right?

281
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:33,159
What does this have to do with you?

282
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:34,840
Psycho.

283
00:14:36,159 --> 00:14:36,799
Don't go yet.

284
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:39,359
Fine.

285
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:41,440
Then I'll tell you.

286
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,440
But you must not tell anyone else.

287
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,359
If I tell you this,

288
00:14:48,359 --> 00:14:49,520
you'll definitely think I'm

289
00:14:50,559 --> 00:14:51,960
very weird and crazy.

290
00:14:53,159 --> 00:14:54,440
But everything I'm saying is true.

291
00:14:56,559 --> 00:14:57,640
Inside my body,

292
00:15:00,719 --> 00:15:01,960
lives another person.

293
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,679
Lives another person?

294
00:15:10,719 --> 00:15:11,840
Are you possessed by a ghost?

295
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:13,320
That's exactly how it feels.

296
00:15:14,599 --> 00:15:15,359
Anyway,

297
00:15:16,039 --> 00:15:17,359
after that incident happened,

298
00:15:18,039 --> 00:15:19,400
my body changed.

299
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,880
I always have a special feeling

300
00:15:21,880 --> 00:15:23,280
about certain things.

301
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,679
So my intuition tells me

302
00:15:25,719 --> 00:15:26,880
there's something wrong with this case.

303
00:15:27,799 --> 00:15:28,520
You have to believe me.

304
00:15:28,919 --> 00:15:29,400
Okay?

305
00:15:35,679 --> 00:15:36,080
Hello?

306
00:15:37,799 --> 00:15:38,239
Okay.

307
00:15:38,239 --> 00:15:38,840
Got it.

308
00:15:41,919 --> 00:15:43,640
You're very lucky today, kid.

309
00:15:44,119 --> 00:15:44,840
Let me tell you,

310
00:15:45,119 --> 00:15:46,320
if you come looking for me again,

311
00:15:46,559 --> 00:15:48,320
I definitely won't let you off.

312
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:49,919
Psycho.

313
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:53,719
Officer Lin!

314
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,640
Then you'll definitely reopen this case,

315
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:57,200
right?

316
00:15:58,880 --> 00:16:00,119
You have to believe me!

317
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,080
Officer Lin!

318
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:06,960
When I found out about Uncle Feng,

319
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,440
I rushed over immediately.

320
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:13,840
I felt I should

321
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:15,359
bid him a final farewell.

322
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:22,359
And a final farewell

323
00:16:26,599 --> 00:16:27,479
between you

324
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:30,039
and me.

325
00:16:30,719 --> 00:16:32,039
I can't ignore all this

326
00:16:32,039 --> 00:16:33,280
and continue to face you.

327
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:36,679
I don't know

328
00:16:36,679 --> 00:16:37,679
how we're going to get along in the future.

329
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,000
Just like you said,

330
00:16:42,479 --> 00:16:44,119
we can't even be friends anymore.

331
00:16:45,559 --> 00:16:47,000
I didn't expect the words I once said

332
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:49,679
to become a sharp blade stabbing me now.

333
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,320
To think I dug myself

334
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,280
such a trap.

335
00:16:58,400 --> 00:17:00,440
Thank you for taking care of me all these years.

336
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:05,760
From now on, we don't owe each other anything.

337
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:31,280
What is Gu Tiancheng doing?

338
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:32,800
Acting so weird all day.

339
00:17:44,319 --> 00:17:44,880
Hello,

340
00:17:45,359 --> 00:17:47,680
the number you have dialed is powered off.

341
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:51,640
Brat.

342
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,079
Her phone is off whenever I look for her.

343
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:04,839
To deal with the bond maturity issue now,

344
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:07,280
we need to produce new products by the first of next month.

345
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:08,479
And the quality inspection

346
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:09,800
must be completed within two weeks.

347
00:18:10,839 --> 00:18:11,400
Jiaqi.

348
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:12,880
Why is your phone turned off?

349
00:18:13,719 --> 00:18:14,199
Also,

350
00:18:14,839 --> 00:18:15,599
Gu Tiancheng,

351
00:18:15,800 --> 00:18:17,000
he's just an idiot, right?

352
00:18:17,520 --> 00:18:18,959
Is there something wrong with him?

353
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:22,479
Jiaqi.

354
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:26,800
No.

355
00:18:27,359 --> 00:18:27,760
It's nothing.

356
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:29,319
Um, sorry.

357
00:18:29,520 --> 00:18:30,319
I'll turn it off right away.

358
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:31,400
Weiwei,

359
00:18:32,479 --> 00:18:33,239
turn off the projector.

360
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:36,119
Today's new product presentation ends here.

361
00:18:37,079 --> 00:18:37,479
Next,

362
00:18:37,959 --> 00:18:38,719
everyone think about it,

363
00:18:39,439 --> 00:18:40,359
does anyone have anything to say?

364
00:18:49,280 --> 00:18:50,239
I'm really sorry.

365
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:52,439
President Gu.

366
00:18:52,599 --> 00:18:53,400
I'll leave you two to talk.

367
00:18:57,359 --> 00:18:59,280
For such a problem to occur on this occasion,

368
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,959
I feel really bad about it.

369
00:19:01,880 --> 00:19:02,439
And...

370
00:19:03,119 --> 00:19:04,119
thank you.

371
00:19:04,719 --> 00:19:05,560
Why are you thanking me?

372
00:19:08,239 --> 00:19:09,839
Thank you for helping me out.

373
00:19:10,239 --> 00:19:10,800
It's nothing.

374
00:19:11,719 --> 00:19:12,239
By the way,

375
00:19:12,760 --> 00:19:13,640
these past few days,

376
00:19:14,079 --> 00:19:14,959
how have you been feeling?

377
00:19:19,520 --> 00:19:20,439
I'm fine.

378
00:19:21,599 --> 00:19:22,439
Liar.

379
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:24,680
You clearly look like something's wrong.

380
00:19:30,439 --> 00:19:31,439
You're a girl,

381
00:19:32,959 --> 00:19:34,040
why do you have to pretend to be strong?

382
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:37,000
Why do you insist on carrying everything yourself?

383
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:38,359
Can you even handle it?

384
00:19:39,079 --> 00:19:39,839
Aren't you tired?

385
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:44,760
You always make people worry.

386
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:52,560
Why are you just standing there?

387
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:54,439
I'm heading home.

388
00:19:55,319 --> 00:19:55,959
I'll drop you off on the way.

389
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:57,199
That's not necessary.

390
00:20:06,119 --> 00:20:07,520
I'm sorry, President Gu.

391
00:20:08,079 --> 00:20:09,439
Because a lot has happened lately...

392
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:10,560
Stop, stop.

393
00:20:12,199 --> 00:20:12,839
On this whole ride,

394
00:20:12,839 --> 00:20:13,719
you've already apologized

395
00:20:13,719 --> 00:20:14,599
I don't know how many times.

396
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:16,520
I'm sorry.

397
00:20:21,439 --> 00:20:22,119
Lin Jiaqi,

398
00:20:23,119 --> 00:20:24,400
is your life

399
00:20:24,719 --> 00:20:26,319
just about saying sorry?

400
00:20:29,199 --> 00:20:30,239
You always say

401
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:32,560
I'm like a child who won't grow up,

402
00:20:33,119 --> 00:20:34,319
that I don't understand others' feelings,

403
00:20:35,079 --> 00:20:35,959
can't take care of people,

404
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:37,400
and that I'm annoying.

405
00:20:37,959 --> 00:20:38,839
But at the very least,

406
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:41,119
I think I live quite happily.

407
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:44,520
What about you?

408
00:20:47,599 --> 00:20:49,439
If a person acts too much like an adult

409
00:20:50,119 --> 00:20:51,599
and cares too much about others' feelings,

410
00:20:52,359 --> 00:20:53,800
then are you happy yourself?

411
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,640
Every one of us

412
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:58,239
only has one life.

413
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,239
We must treat it well.

414
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:03,239
If you dedicate your life

415
00:21:03,239 --> 00:21:04,280
entirely to others,

416
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:06,479
making everyone else happy,

417
00:21:07,239 --> 00:21:08,160
and making everyone think

418
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,959
that Lin Jiaqi is a great person,

419
00:21:11,439 --> 00:21:12,280
then what about yourself?

420
00:21:12,959 --> 00:21:14,640
How much time do you leave for yourself?

421
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,800
Before, you had Du Zheng

422
00:21:18,959 --> 00:21:19,800
to care for you

423
00:21:20,199 --> 00:21:20,839
and comfort you.

424
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,880
But after Du Zheng left?

425
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,479
I know you just try desperately to bear it,

426
00:21:26,479 --> 00:21:27,479
desperately enduring it.

427
00:21:28,959 --> 00:21:29,719
Lin Jiaqi,

428
00:21:32,959 --> 00:21:34,319
stop pushing yourself so hard, okay?

429
00:21:35,959 --> 00:21:37,359
Du Zheng died on that cold ground

430
00:21:37,359 --> 00:21:38,640
not that long ago.

431
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:39,800
Why do I feel like

432
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:41,640
you've forgotten him so quickly?

433
00:21:42,359 --> 00:21:43,040
Do you understand?

434
00:21:44,800 --> 00:21:45,359
I'm sorry.

435
00:21:45,359 --> 00:21:46,680
I don't know what you're talking about.

436
00:21:46,959 --> 00:21:47,599
I'll get going.

437
00:21:48,079 --> 00:21:48,680
Lin Jiaqi.

438
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:52,599
Silly girl.

439
00:21:53,319 --> 00:21:54,880
You don't have to pretend around me anymore.

440
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:58,040
You can lean on my shoulder anytime.

441
00:21:58,359 --> 00:21:59,719
If you're sad, just cry it out.

442
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:02,199
From now on, everything,

443
00:22:04,719 --> 00:22:06,119
I will share the burden with you.
